Laboratory Analysis for Metabolic

Usage

adlb_metabolic

Format

Study Identifier

DOMAIN

Domain Abbreviation

USUBJID

Unique Subject Identifier

LBSEQ

Sequence Number

LBTESTCD

Lab Test or Examination Short Name

LBTEST

Lab Test or Examination Name

LBCAT

Category for Lab Test

LBORRES

Result or Finding in Original Units

LBORRESU

Original Units

LBORNRLO

LBORNRHI

Reference Range Upper Limit in Orig Unit

LBSTRESC

Character Result/Finding in Std Format

LBSTRESN

Numeric Result/Finding in Standard Units

Standard Units

LBSTNRLO

LBSTNRHI

LBNRIND

Reference Range Indicator

LBBLFL

Baseline Flag

LBFAST

Fasting Status

VISITNUM

Visit Number

VISIT

VISITDY

LBDTC

LBDY

TRTSDT

TRTEDT

Date of Last Exposure to Treatment

TRT01P

PARAMCD

PARAM

Parameter

PARAMN

Parameter (N)

ADT

ADY

AVISIT

AVISITN

PARCAT1

Source

Generated from admiralmetabolic package (template ad_adlb.R).

Details

Contains a set of 11 unique Parameter Codes and Parameters:

PARAMCDPARAM
ALBAlbumin (g/L)
ALKPHAlkaline Phosphatase (U/L)
ASTAspartate Aminotransferase (U/L)
CHOLESCholesterol (mmol/L)
FLIFatty Liver Index
GGTGamma Glutamyl Transferase (U/L)
GLUCGlucose (mmol/L)
HBA1CHGBHemoglobin A1C/Hemoglobin (mmol/mol)
HOMAIRHomeostasis Model Assessment - Insulin Resistance
INSULINInsulin (mIU/L)
TRIGTriglycerides (mg/dL)

None
